<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.5.2">
<l>māri mākkaṭal vaḷaivaṇaṟ kiḷaiyavaṉ 	varaipurai tirumārpil</l>
<l>tāri ṉācaiyil pōyiṉa neñcamum tāḻntatōr tuṇaikāṇēṉ</l>
<l>ūrum tuñciṟṟu lakamum tuyiṉṟa toḷiyavaṉ vicumpiyaṅkum</l>
<l>tērum pōyiṟṟut ticaikaḷum maṟaintaṉa ceyvatoṉ ṟaṟiyēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even [my] heart, which left in desire for the garland</l>
<l rend="indent">on the mountain-like divine chest</l>
<l>Of the younger brother of the one the color of a conch</l>
<l rend="indent">in the rain[-filled] dark sea, stayed [there];</l>
<l>I do not find  any help! The city slumbers; the world also sleeps.</l>
<l rend="indent">Even the chariot of the sun  which moves in the heavens</l>
<l>Has vanished; all directions are shrouded. I do not know what to do!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
